      <title>耶伦认为期限溢价将上升，利率重新定价是收益率上升的推动因素</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/yellen-sees-term-premium-rise-rate-repricing-behind-yield-climb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特耶伦表示，强于预期的经济数据刺激了对利率预期的重新定价，导致美国国债遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/yellen-sees-term-premium-rise-rate-repricing-behind-yield-climb</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 16:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
