      <title>马萨诸塞州新法对私募股权投资施加新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/massachusetts-enacts-new-curbs-on-private-equity-in-health-care</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据马萨诸塞州州长莫拉·希利（Maura Healey）周三签署的一项新法律，医疗保健行业的私募股权投资者将面临额外的监管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/massachusetts-enacts-new-curbs-on-private-equity-in-health-care</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 12:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街准备迎接就业市场动荡，股市动荡：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票交易员不愿进行大举押注，市场将在周五就业报告公布前夕收盘，预计该报告将为美联储降息步伐提供线索。美国国债收益率近期飙升后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 22:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒冷天气导致市场紧张，英国电价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/uk-warns-of-tight-power-market-as-deep-freeze-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国电网运营商今天下午发布市场警告，由于风力发电量下降导致供应减少，而气温骤降导致需求增加，电价随后飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/uk-warns-of-tight-power-market-as-deep-freeze-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 21:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
